content:
Great puzzle! Definitely not "easy", I would classify it as "medium" as there are lots of edge cases and instructions. Alternatively I would suggest to simplify it so that it is "easy":

* removing the starting corner and direction, and having it always be `topLeft` and `clockwise`;
* have only one "short string" like `D3` and make the letters always grow by one;
* and size always < 31 as a constraint.

With any of those changes I'd approve it (but I still have a few levels to go for that).
